HADITH CONTENT NOTICE

The hadith texts included in this project are sourced from the authenticated
books of the Sunnah (Sahih al-Bukhari, Sahih Muslim, and other canonical
collections). These texts are part of the Islamic scholarly heritage and are
not subject to copyright. They are reproduced here solely for educational,
spiritual, and non-commercial informational purposes.

All translations are provided for accessibility and ease of understanding.
Users are encouraged to verify hadith authenticity through recognised Islamic
scholars and established hadith databases (e.g., sunnah.com).
